$title[0] 	= "Rank: Provost";
$banner[0] 	= "<img src=\"../images/banner_provost.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\"/>";
$rnk_p11[0]	= "The <b>provost</b>, for all intent and purposes, within the context of the Academy, is the Academy's <b>maestro</b> or <b>master</b>.  Without a formal title of <b>maestro</b> conveyed to the provost by the an existing <b>master</b> of the art, the provost cannot use the title of maestro or master externally to the Academy.";
$rnk_p12[0]	= "First and foremost, the <b>provost</b> must have a proven track record in the instruction of the art, and is skilled in all weapons as described by Fiore dei Liberi's treatise.  The <b>provost</b> has developed an intimate understanding of the different characteristics, underlying principles and theoretical approaches to each of the weapons and fighting styles described.  This individual has obtained this rank after a minimum of eight (8) years of study and training.  Key responsibilities of the <b>provost</b> is the training and teaching of students, and the contribution to the general operations and/or administration functions of the Academy.  An official teaching license or letter is granted by the Academy governing body to those who have successfully prized at this rank.";
$rnk_p13[0]	= "The <b>provost</b> also must abide by the rules, similar to those rules of the <b>maestro</b> which describes ones responsibilities of this rank, which includes stating one's allegiance and loyalties to the organization (in this case, to the Academy), and an all-encompassing code of conduct and behaviour which the <b>provost</b> is expected to abide by within the context of historical martial arts.  The <b>provost</b> must abide by the rules and constitution of the Academy, and promote the principles of historical martial arts and organizations that are focused on the formalization of these arts.";

$title_p2[0] 	= "Provost Requirements";
$rnk_l21[0]	= "\"time in\" as free scholler of a minimum of five (5) years,";
$rnk_l22[0]	= "demonstrated teaching skill in both individually-oriented training and group-oriented training sessions";
$rnk_l23[0]	= "has delivered instruction to regularly scheduled classes,";
$rnk_l24[0]	= "possesses a solid analytical understanding of the historical treatises relevant to the art of <i>armizare</i>,";
$rnk_l25[0]	= "possesses skill in multiple weapons as described in Fiore dei Liberi's treatise,";
$rnk_l26[0]	= "earned a minimum of level 1 <a href=\"http://www.coach.ca/coach-training-in-canada-s15408\" target=\"_blank\"><b>NCCP</b></a> certification,";
$rnk_l27[0]	= "title of <b>provost</b> conveyed by the Academy's governing body,";
$rnk_l28[0]	= "the <b>provost</b> candidate has been assessed and observed by the Academy's senior members and executive through time of the candidate's abilities with respect to all aspects of <b>armizare</b> as described by Fiore dei Liberi, and most importantly, their instruction and teaching capabilities,";
$rnk_l29[0]	= "must be of at least 30 years of age,";
$rnk_l210[0]	= "the candidate is considered if the following are satisfied:";
$rnk_l211[0]	= "demonstrated knowledge of fencing & fight theory by responding to queries by the Academy's governing body or by his/her peers,";
$rnk_l212[0]	= "demonstrated teaching skill by giving an individual lesson(s) and group lesson(s) to the other candidates or students identified by the Academy's senior members and governing body,";
$rnk_l213[0]	= "demonstrated fencing and fighting proficiency in the art of <i>armizare</i>,";
$rnk_l214[0]	= "demonstrated knowledge of hopology by analysis of a weapon chosen randomly by the Academy's governing body or by his/her peers,";
$rnk_l215[0]	= "formally makes the request to the governing body of his/her intention for the rank of <b>provost</b>.";
$rnk_l216[0]	= "has submitted at least one or more research papers submission to the Academy's governing body, its review and acceptance.";
$rnk_l217[0]	= "is prepared to participate in the Academy's governing body.";

$title_p3[0] 	= "Responsibilities of a Provost";
$rnk_l31[0]	= "deliver instruction and training to students of all ranks in regularly scheduled classes,";
$rnk_l32[0]	= "actively participates in the general operational and administrative aspects of the Academy (assist in the defining guildelines, rules, policy making, program development, etc.) in a role defined by the executive as an advisor or officer,</li><li>representation of the Academy or chapter at symposiums, workshops and conferences as a lecturer, presenter, trainer,";
$rnk_l33[0]	= "actively participates on one or more external governing bodies and entities as an advisor, board member, etc.,";
$rnk_l34[0]	= "participate in the ranking of students and their designation within the Academy at the <b>free scholler</b> and <b>provost</b> ranks only,";
$rnk_l35[0]	= "participate in the ranking of students in other schools upon invitation by that school at the <b>free scholler</b> and <b>provost</b> ranks only,";
$rnk_l36[0]	= "to liaise with specific academic and or museum institutions (with permission from Academy's governing body),";
$rnk_l37[0]	= "to liaise with other training academies (assume the role as the primary contact within the Academy for one or two other training academies) (with permission from Academy's governing body),";
$rnk_l38[0]	= "participate and contribute in creating and implementing policies within the Academy and the external governing body,";
$rnk_l39[0]	= "has submitted one or more research papers on a relevant subject and which has been accepted by the Academy's governing body and which has been published in the <a href=\"../onlineResources/whitePapers/research_papers_body.htm\">Research\White Papers</a> area of the web, as well as the <a href=\"http://jwma.ejmas.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Journal of Western Martial Art</a> and other publications.";

$title_p4[0] 	= "Skill Development and Training Specifications for Free Scholler";
$rnk_l4a[0]	= "<b>Theory</b>";
$rnk_l41[0]	= "significant contributions and/or enhancements to the formulation, evolution and structure of <i>l`arte dell`armizare</i> or other fighting arts discipline, e.g. sword & shield training, German unarmoured longsword, quarterstaff or some other relevant fighting style,";
$rnk_l42[0]	= "engage on the study of another historical treatise (e.g. Vadi, Ringeck, etc.), and the possibility of either a) a learned article on the treatise; b) development and inclusion of the art described into the AEMMA training program,";
$rnk_l43[0]	= "refinement of AEMMA's understanding and evolutionary application of new or enhanced concepts into the AEMMA training program.";
$rnk_l4b[0]	= "<b>Technical</b>";
$rnk_l51[0]	= "enhanced swordsmanship skills in terms of winding, binding, thrusting, single-time parry, 1/2-sword, etc.,";
$rnk_l52[0]	= "continued skills development in <i>l`arte dell`armizare</i> or other weapons/fighting disciplines or styles,";
$rnk_l53[0]	= "specializing in a particular <i>armizare</i> fighting style, e.g. armour combat, mounted combat, etc.";

$title_p6[0] 	= "Other Free Scholler Attributes:";
$rnk_l61[0]	= "continued enhancements in one's training in the philosophy and principles in the art of combat, manipulation of the opponent, control of battle, control of opponent, ";
$rnk_l62[0]	= "development of additional <a href=\"trng_body.htm#drills\">drills</a> or <i>sequentia</i> designed to enhance fighting attributes of students,";
$rnk_l63[0]	= "is able to create a startup a chapter of the Academy in a location remote to the parent Academy,";
$rnk_l64[0]	= "contact free-form fencing bouts continue employing steel weapons and possibly sharps,";
$rnk_l65[0]	= "introduction to manipulation of the opponent, internalizing the art of control of the engagement,";
$rnk_l66[0]	= "more and advanced grasping techniques, sword grabbing, defensive to offensive positioning,";
$rnk_l67[0]	= "introduction of alternative weapons combat, e.g. longsword engaged with polearms (halberds, bills, pikes, etc.), longsword engaged with sword &amp; shield, etc.,";
$rnk_l68[0]	= "estimate <b>free scholler</b> training duration and \"time-in\" of a minimum of 2 years,";
